The paper focuses on imitation learning for robots, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses knowledge fusion and transfer learning, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The experiments involve a self-driving task, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and control systems (cs.SY).
